      <br/>
      In almost all cases, reach out to the
      <a href="mailto:rubyhackers@amazon.com">rubyhackers@</a>
      for
      any general questions about Ruby and/or Rails. Want to report a bug or buy us a beer for all of
      this hard work? Contact ruby-core at
      <%= succeed "." do %>
        <a href="mailto:ruby-core@amazon.com">ruby-core@</a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
